menu.link_string: E wehe i ka loulou ma Kasm

text.header1: E wehe i nā loulou me ka palekana a me ka inoa ʻole me ka hoʻohana ʻana iā Kasm Open-in-Isolation.
text.header2: Hāʻawi ka Kasm Open in Isolation browser extension i kahi koho papa kuhikuhi-pololei e wehe i nā loulou pūnaewele ma kahi polokalamu kaʻawale Workspaces. ʻO kēia ka mea maʻalahi a maʻalahi hoʻi ka wehe pono ʻana i nā URL kānalua / palekana a i ʻole e mālama i kāu pilikino. Ma muli o ka hāʻawi ʻia ʻana o ka ʻaoʻao pūnaewele i loko o ka polokalamu kele pūnaewele mamao, ma mua o ka hoʻokō ʻia ʻana ma kāu kamepiula kūloko, hiki iā ʻoe ke launa pū me ka ʻaoʻao pūnaewele me ka palekana a me ka inoa ʻole.
text.header3: E ʻike i ka palapala Kasm no nā kikoʻī hou aku.
text.form2: E hoʻohana i ke kī hoʻolei

title.tooltip1: E wehe ʻo Go i ka URL ma kahi Workspace hou, ʻo ke ʻano Cast Key no kahi papa hana e holo nei
title.tooltip2: I ka wehe ʻana i ka kikokikona ma kahi hālāwai Kasm Workspaces inā ʻaʻole he URL kūpono ke kaula, e hāʻawi ʻia ia i kahi ʻenekini huli.
title.tooltip3: Inā wehe ʻoe i kahi kikokikona ma kahi Workspace makemake paha ʻoe e pani i nā kaula i hāʻawi ʻia i ka Workspace (E ʻimi e kākoʻo i ka RegExp maʻamau me nā delimiters /regexp/g)
